{"tid":1478214,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳班大陸仔落嚟扮示威者殺狗，警犬仲未知驚？","createTime":"2019-08-16T12:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T23:42:29.000Z","uid":78971,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e093a75c5c2be019d61608935cb9024196d23a93","tid":1478214,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:01:01.000Z","msg":"估唔到共產黨係殘忍到咁<br />\n再唔搵晒班大陸仔，到時都唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03655b018970de3871d11b2c59d347162af9c26e","tid":1478214,"uid":237809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9380066fc6c3c533b584cba3cf15b6e3c3334783","tid":1478214,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:25:44.000Z","msg":"犧牲popo<br />\n成全老解"},{"pid":"d1329e61d77f341e4f0a99121168be527b7e25e1","tid":1478214,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"popo回頭是岸"},{"pid":"53bccb3a0e4ddb6c8719f67c604264891a3e2191","tid":1478214,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:31:24.000Z","msg":"分析大家可以點應對818反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475432</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n入黎傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多巴絲對818有諗法！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n總括post入邊大家意見：<br />\n818不衝 不圍 不挑釁 不設防 能放能收 坐爆維園<br />\n<br />\n有手足提出：<br />\n<br />\n1.唔佔馬路 齋坐行人路（坐行人路唔係非法集會？有冇法律手足講下）<br />\n<br />\n2.記得戴定口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同頭盔或帽，保護自己<br />\n全世界帶眼罩<br />\n<br />\n3.如果有人行跡可疑 就示威者手鏈圍大圈 圈入面就記者同幾位勇d嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果冇野大家唔會驚 如果有野就制服佢 搵證據 俾記者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 維園冇位就坐係沿途商埸 一齊睇live 順便幫人哋罷市<br />\n<br />\n5. 避開坐爆之前同黑社會發生衝突嘅位置，避免引起衝突，恐慌<br />\n<br />\n6. 無論所有交通工具都金鐘落，行去維園，行唔到就坐<br />\n<br />\n7. 64當年有軍火隨街放，大家記住唔好拎同點！唔好俾藉囗中共鎮壓<br />\n<br />\n8. -出得嚟就要同自己打定最壞打算，無論咩人都係<br />\n-要克服你嘅恐慌 有突發事出現，<br />\n同隔離嗰個一齊分擔<br />\n-唔好因爲緊張亂講野，唔好因爲緊張亂信人<br />\n9.夠鐘就散場 下次再遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n試下說 勇武手法/和理非手法<br />\n任何手足都可以唔同場合，用唔同手法做事架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc7f62a1a47cdc949b2abe9437612fe80ee9d94","tid":1478214,"uid":236173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"popo回頭是岸"},{"pid":"2fe5e3e2ff69a16d9aa87ec309d1b0534eb4a5ff","tid":1478214,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:42:29.000Z","msg":"popo回頭是岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈傳愈勁呀"}]}